        "detailedDescription_md": "The scheme &amp;quot;Interest Subsidy Scheme on Education Loan&amp;quot; by the Education Department, Government of Gujarat, aims to provide complete financial relief to students through 100% interest subsidy on education loans for the entire moratorium period. This includes the study period and 1 additional year after course completion.\n<br>\n\n",
        "benefits_md": "\n- **Interest Subsidy Assistance:** 100% interest subsidy on education loans up to ₹10,00,000/- for the moratorium period (course duration + 1 year).\n<br>\n\n",
