          "process_md": "> **Registration Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** Visit the [Official Website](https://kcg.gujarat.gov.in/education_loan/student_login/sign_up.php) and fill in all the details.\n**Step 2:** Set an username and password.\n**Step 3:** Verify the details and click on &quot;Register&quot;.\n> **Application Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** Visit the [Official Website](https://kcg.gujarat.gov.in/education_loan/student_login/login.php) and enter the username and password.\n**Step 2:** Enter all relavant details and fill out the online form.\n**Step 3:** Upload all required documents in the specified format if required.\n**Step 4:** Click on &quot;Submit&quot; to comlete the applicaion process.\n**Step 5:** After completing the full details of the application-submitting your application formprint the acknowledgment receipt.\n**Step 6:** The applicant will have to print the acknowledgment receipt and according to checklist\nall Documents send it to the KCG either directly or by courier (all the documents should be selfattested).\n> **Contact Us:**\n\n**Kcg E-Mail Id:** isel-kcg[at]gujgov[dot]edu[dot]in\n**Helpline No:** 9909039380 (10:30 AM to 6:00 PM)\n<br>\n\n"
