        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n   1. The applicant must be a resident of Gujarat.\n   1. The applicant must be a student.\n   1. The applicant must have passed HSC (Higher Secondary Certificate) with at least 60 percentile.\n   1. The applicant must have taken an education loan from a recognized bank for pursuing higher education in India or abroad.\n   1. The applicant must have a family income not exceeding ₹6,00,000/- per year.\n\n<br>\n\n",
